MIME media type name : Application

MIME subtype name : Vendor Tree - vnd.cab-jscript

Required parameters : none

Optional parameters : none

Encoding considerations : binary
This media type may require encoding on transports not capable of handling binary.

Security considerations :
Delivery of this format to a printer which is not capable of parsing the format may 
result in poor printer behavior. The media type doesn't contain executable content, 
nor does it need privacy. It can however be used to transfer the source code of BASIC 
programs which are executed in a sandbox in the printer.

Interoperability considerations :
none

Published specification :
cab Programming Manual Thermal/Thermal Transfer Printers

http://www.cabgmbh.com/deutsch/downloads/kennzeichnung/pdf/ProgmanE51a.pdf

Applications which use this media :
Windows printer drivers, label printing software
